In Re Gary Ray BOWLES, petitioner.
No. 19-5682 (19A217).
Supreme Court of the United States
Aug. 22, 2019.
Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice THOMAS and by him referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of habeas corpus denied.
